data.description: This charming home in East Lake has amazing potential. With 1500 square feet of living space the possibilities are endless in this spacious beauty. The laundry room has the potential to be converted into a 2nd bathroom and is adjacent to the master bedroom. This home has seen updates recently. The original windows have been restored, allowing for a lot of natural light. The kitchen has new vinyl flooring, countertops, and a tile backsplash. The bathroom has a new vanity and toilet. The seller has also added a new front storm door and fresh paint inside and out. Don't miss this opportunity, schedule your showing today.
